This episode of HashiCast features Cheryl Hung from StorageOS.

Cheryl is a product manager at StorageOS where she leads the DevOps engineering team who ship a world-class product for running enterprise databases with Kubernetes in production.  She is also a Cloud Native ambassador and organized the Cloud Native Meetup in London.

Join us as we chat the complexities with managing storage in a container based world, why sometimes immutable is just not enough.

